{"id":267254,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/12/维权网-四川杨积静遭遇征地强拆到北京上访被暴/","date":"2012-12-08T07:31:24Z","modified":"2012-12-08T07:31:24Z","title":"维权网 | 四川杨积静遭遇征地强拆到北京上访被暴打（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员陈华报道）四川省绵阳市经开区红塔街的杨积静，继</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日</span><span>从北京上访回来被暴打后，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日</span><span>再次到北京上访。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日</span><span>，从久敬庄被驻京办送回绵阳，由街道办许大志、王小琴、汤秀珍将其押回。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2008</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月，绵阳市政府为了城市开发，将原涪城区石塘乡南塔村</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>组农民的土地全部征用，其中，征用杨积静土地</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1.5</span><span>亩，拆迁楼房</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">613.69</span><span>平米，每平米只给</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">240</span><span>元的赔付。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日</span><span>凌晨</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>点钟，经开区政府</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>来人，强行将尚在睡梦中的杨积静夫妇拖出屋外，用挖掘机摧毁了杨积静的房屋和土地。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>几年来，杨积静四处上访。今年以来，又向绵阳市政府、经开区政府提出申诉，要求：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>、依法补偿全部补偿费用和上访费用，共计人民币</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">841</span><span>，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span><span>元；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>、落实《四川省计划生育条例》规定独生子女宅基地</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>平米；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>、按规定发放安置就业补偿等各项费用。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日</span><span>，杨积静从北京上访回来的第二天，在绵阳市经星市场公交车站等车，被所在的街道办、村领导</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>来人围堵，其中，三个戴口罩的小伙子冲上前来，一掌将杨积静推翻在地，拿出钢棒，对着杨积静一阵暴打，站在旁边的老公被拖走。杨积静一边大喊救命，一边奋力抢夺钢棒。一时间，杨积静全身被打得青紫，手腕、腿腕上更是血痕累累。打了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>来分钟，凶手跳上一辆乳白色的轿车跑了。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>事后，政府到处放风说：杨积静的脚、手都被打断了，这下不敢到处上访了。杨积静听后，于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日</span><span>再次到北京上访，以证明自己坚持维权的决心和勇气。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>杨积静电话</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 13778148773</span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-FS9Al6wiItI/UMKhvpInF0I/AAAAAAAAVfk/X9P_FWXV0FQ/s1600/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE00.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"224\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-FS9Al6wiItI/UMKhvpInF0I/AAAAAAAAVfk/X9P_FWXV0FQ/s320/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE00.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-1349406553429864220?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}